quran[13{c,v,t}:
27,23,mein ne wahan aik aurat dekhi jo is qoum ki hukmaran hai uss ko har terhan ka saaz o samaan bakhsha gaya hai aur is ka takhat bara azeem al shan hai
27,24,"mein ne dekha hai ke woh aur is ki qoum Allah ke bajaye Sooraj ke agay sajda karti hai"" shetan ne un ke aamaal un ke liye khushnuma bana diye aur inhen shahrah se rok diya, is wajah se woh yeh seedha rasta nahi paate"
27,25,ke uss khuda ko sajda karen jo asmano aur zameen ki posheeda cheeze nikalta hai aur woh sab kuch jaanta hai jisay tum log chupatay ho aur zahir karte ho
27,26,"Allah ke jis ke siwa koi mustahiq ibadat nahi, jo arsh azeem ka maalik hai"
27,27,"sulaiman ne kaha"" abhi hum dekhe letay hain ke to ne sach kaha hai ya to jhoot bolnay walon mein se hai"
27,28,"mera yeh khat le ja aur usay un logon ki taraf daal day, phir allag hatt kar dekh ke woh kya radd amal zahir karte hain """
27,29,"malka boli"" ae ehley darbaar, meri taraf aik bara ahem khat phenka gaya hai"
27,30,woh sulaiman ki janib se hai aur Allah rehman o Raheem ke naam se shuru kya gaya hai
27,31,"mazmoon yeh hai ke “meraymuqablay mein sar kashi nah karo aur muslim ho kar mere paas haazir ho jao """
27,32,"( khat suna kar ) malka ne kaha"" “ay sardaran qoum mere is muamlay mein mujhe mahswara do, mein kisi maamla ka faisla tumahray baghair nahi karti hon """
27,33,"onhon ne jawab diya"" hum taaqat war aur larnay walay log hain agay faisla aap ke haath mein hai aap khud dekh len ke aap ko kya hukum dena hai """
27,34,"malka ne kaha ke"" badshah jab kisi mulk mein ghis atay hain to usay kharab aur is ke izzat walon ko zaleel kar dete hain yahi kuch woh kya karte hain"
27,35,"mein inn logon ki taraf aik Hadia bhijti hon, phir dekhatii hon ke mere alchi kya jawab le kar palatne hain """
